description:
You have asked for it so here it is!  The Flokati Rug is the perfect addition to your studio!  Who loves free shipping?  Yes, that's right we are offering our Flokati Rugs with FREE SHIPPING.

This Flokati is made without the typical rug backing to allow the rug to be draped like a blanket over bean bags for newborn portraits!  This is a favorite with our newborn photographers!

The rug is made with a 1400 gram wool pile. Machine washable, lay flat to dry and brush to fluff.   

We offer these in a multitude of colors - with some new ones coming soon! 
 
Available in TWO sizes - 
Small - 3ft 6in by 5ft 6in.  $150
Large - 5 ft by 8 ft. $350

Choose from:  Burgundy, Olive, Black, Pink, Lt. Blue, Cocoa, Denim, Lime, Cream, Tan, Fuschia, Red.  -- Watch for more colors to come!

This item will be drop shipped to you FREE via UPS typically within 2 to 3 weeks within the USA - sometimes sooner.  International Orders please email us for a shipping quote. 

TIPS on Washing your Rug:
Set your machine to a delicate cycle. Feel free to add a touch of mild soap generally used for woolens. You can also add a bit of liquid softener as desired. 
Once the cycle is complete, hang dry your rug until completely dry. 

DO NOT place your Flokati rug in a dryer. And remember to try and avoid direct sunlight when possible. Once dry, brush the Flokati rug with a metal (dog) brush, beginning at the center of the rug and working your way outward. 

This will help to "fluff" the Flokati rug and keep it looking and feeling full and plush!
